Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Coron School of Fisheries in the Municipality of Coron, Province of Palawan, to Assemblyman Claudio R. Sandoval School of Fisheries
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 235
An Act Changing the Name of the Coron School of Fisheries in the Municipality of Coron, Province of Palawan, to Assemblyman Claudio R. Sandoval School of Fisheries
Section 1. The name of the Coron School of Fisheries in the Municipality of Coron, Province of Palawan, is hereby changed to Assemblyman Claudio R. Sandoval School of fisheries.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: September 12, 1982
